<ab facs="#facs_272_r1l25">ew <expan>geſa<ex>n</ex>t</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> der nam <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> als den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan></del> <expan>geſcheh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_272_r1l26">ıſt / . <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vns die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vvol <expan>embot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>cʒevviſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> getan / vvie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_272_r1l27">Jr Jn <expan>darynne<ex>n</ex></expan> vaſt hılfflıch vnd fürderlıch <expan>geweſe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeit / des wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_272_r1l28"><expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel cʒemal <expan>fleiʒʒikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr ewr hılffe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_272_r1l29">vnd fürdrung auch fürbas dar cʒü tün wollet / damit es </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_272_r1l31">den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
